message: "If you use DissolvA in your work, please cite it as below."
title: "DissolvA: Predictive Dissolution Suite"
abstract: >-
  A web-based pharmaceutical dissolution analysis platform: FDA/EMA
  guidance-aligned f1/f2 similarity, 62 kinetic models, bootstrap f2, USP
  monograph compliance checks, and professional reporting. Proprietary software,
  available as a hosted service at https://www.dissolva.app.
type: software
authors:
